station-event-bluespace-tdf-vault-start-announcement = A TDF high security supply-vault is inbound to the sector. The TDF may declare the vault a restricted No Fly Zone. Auric Outpost and station accounts will be rewarded for its safe transit.
station-event-bluespace-tdf-vault-warning-announcement = Remote FTL procedures initialized, five minutes until vault extraction.
station-event-bluespace-tdf-vault-end-announcement = Vault has been retrieved from this area of Triad space. Auric Outpost and station accounts have been subsidized.

station-event-bluespace-generic-ftl-start-announcement = Attention all Triad sector citizens! Triad Sector Monitoring has detected an unidentified vessel entering the Triad Sector. Investigate with caution, you may be at risk of harm or loss of life.
station-event-bluespace-generic-ftl-warning-announcement = Remote FTL procedures initialized, five minutes until unidentified vessel dissipation.
station-event-bluespace-generic-ftl-end-announcement = To ensure safer passage in FTL traffic patterns, the unidentified vessel has been dissipated to ensure non-collision.

station-event-bluespace-syndi-cache-start-announcement = A Syndicate weapons cache has been spotted FTL travelling into the sector. Recommendation: destruction of the cache.
station-event-bluespace-syndi-cache-start-radio-announcement = A Spinward Syndicate weapons cache was spotted in the sector. Recommended actions: Seizure of smuggled goods, destruction of cache. Use local mercenary help wherever necessary; do not let the Syndicate remnants prosper.
station-event-bluespace-syndi-cache-warning-announcement = We've detected activity from the Syndicate cache's FTL drive, estimated five minutes until the cache exits the sector.
station-event-bluespace-syndi-cache-end-announcement = The Syndicate weapons cache has left the sector. Return to previous duties.

station-event-bluespace-name-TDFVault = High-Sec TDF Vault
